          "process_md": "***Interested applicants can submit their applications in the prescribed format (available at the IDTR office) in offline mode at the Institute of Driving and Traffic Research (IDTR), Dehradun.***\n***Required Documents for Light Motor Vehicle (Vocational Course):***\n\n  - Aadhaar card of the applicant.\n  - Caste certificate of the applicant.\n  - One recent passport-size photograph.\n  - High School Certificate or 8th Class Transfer Certificate.\n  - A valid Light Motor Vehicle (Non-Transport) Driving License, at least one year old.\n\n***For Heavy Vehicle (Vocational Course):***\n\n  - Aadhaar card of the applicant.\n  - Caste certificate of the applicant.\n  - One recent passport-size photograph.\n  - High School Certificate or 8th Class Transfer Certificate.\n  - A valid Light Motor Vehicle (Transport) Driving License.\n  - The license must be at least one year old.\n\n***For Refresher Courses:***\n\n  - Aadhaar card of the applicant.\n\n&gt; **A valid Driving License to operate a Light or Heavy Motor Vehicle.**\n\n**Validity:** There is no time limit.\n**Renewal:** It is not required.\n**Fees:** Free of cost.\n**Process:** Applications are scrutinized, and eligible candidates are admitted to the training program on a first-come, first-served basis.\n**Process:** Applications can be submitted throughout the year, and training commences as soon as batches are formed.\n<br>\n\n"
        }
